response.original_title: The Golden Age of Looney Tunes - Volume 1: 1930s Musicals
response.overview: Smile, Darn Ya, Smile (in B&W); Shuffle Off to Buffalo (in B&W); Miss Glory; I Love to Singa; Have You Got Any Castles; Speaking of the Weather; and Katnip Kollege are the 7 complete uncut musical cartoons included in this fun-filled VHS.
